Interface Mappable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    City, PointOfInterest

    public interface Mappable
    Project #5 CS 2334, Section 10 April 22, 2014 Interface to contain all actions that a 'mappable' region should be able to perform. A 'mappable' region is one that has coordinates.
    Version:
    1.0
